386→                        <div id="content">Let $f(n;r,k)$ be the maximal number of edges in an $r$-uniform hypergraph which contains no set of $k$ many independent edges. <br><br>For all $r\geq 3$,\[f(n;r,k)=\max\left(\binom{rk-1}{r}, \binom{n}{r}-\binom{n-k+1}{r}\right).\]</div>
387→                        <div id="problem_id"><a href="/1020">#1020</a>: <a href="#cite-Er65d-1020" onclick="event.preventDefault();addNewBox('Er65d','1020'); return false;">[Er65d]</a><a href="#cite-Er71-1020" onclick="event.preventDefault();addNewBox('Er71','1020'); return false;">[Er71,p.103]</a></div>
